item.description:
Here are some quotes that are particularly impactful to me:
 &ldquo;Adopt the pace of nature: her secret is patience.&rdquo;
~ Ralph Waldo Emerson
&ldquo;In every walk with nature one receives far more than he seeks.&rdquo;
~ John Muir
&ldquo;Only by going alone in silence, without baggage, can one truly get into the heart of the wilderness. All other travel is mere dust and hotels and baggage and chatter.&rdquo;
~ John Muir
